Message.En: Efforts Shall Not Go to Waste
Message.Jp: 努力を無にしたくない

Message.En:
Yesterday, in the name of the White Knights' honor,
I took down <LQVA> <LQEM> during my free time.
However, due to mission constraints,
I won't be able to go outside today.
If I skip the hunt, the number of them
will increase again.
I'm sorry, but could someone please
take down the same number for me?
Message.Jp:
昨日は白騎団の誇りにかけ、自由時間に<LQEM>を<LQVA>体討伐した
しかし今日は任務の都合上、外に出られそうにないのだ
討伐を休むとまた個体数が増えてしまう
すまないが、誰か同じ分だけ討伐しておいてくれないだろうか
